7. "två" is a determiner for "filtar."
8. "stora" is an adjective modifying "filtar."
9. "filtar" is a direct object of "bär."
10. "att sitta" is an infinitive phrase acting as a complement to "filtar."
11. "på" is a preposition which "sitta" depends on, making "på" its head.
12. "Bojt" is the subject of the third clause.
13. "får" is the main verb of this clause.
14. "hjälpa" is the infinitive verb and is related to "får."
15. "pappa" is the direct object of "hjälpa."
16. "att bära" is another infinitive phrase serving as a complement to "hjälpa."
17. "metsöna" is the direct object of "bära."

